# Tool Configuration

Configure your specific tools below. Commands and agents reference this file
for tool-specific details.

Copy this file to `tools.md` in the same directory and fill in your values.

## Ticket System

- **Tool**: (e.g., Linear MCP, Jira MCP, GitHub Issues)
- **MCP fetch command**: (e.g., `mcp__linear-server__get_issue`)
- **MCP comments command**: (e.g., `mcp__linear-server__list_comments`)
- **URL pattern**: (e.g., `https://linear.app/org/issue/ID/...`)
- **ID format**: (e.g., `PB-752`, `PROJ-123`)

## Workspace (optional)

Override the default workspace directory (`.ai-workspace/`):
- **Directory**: (e.g., `tmp`, `.workspace`, `_tickets`)

## Git Provider Overrides (optional)

Git provider and CLI tool are auto-detected from `git remote get-url origin`:
- `github.com` → `gh`
- `gitlab.com` → `glab`

Only add overrides here for self-hosted instances or non-standard setups:

```
git.mycompany.com = gh
gitlab.internal.co = glab
```

